metadata.name: Dune
metadata.description:
Dune is a project that draws inspiration from classic fantasy and science fiction literature, films, and art. 

Shot mainly using expired films, The aim of the project is to create a body of work that transports the audience into an ethereal realm that is both familiar and otherworldly with a sense of nostalgia and futuristic in the same time. 

The project challenges the viewers to explore their own imaginations and consider the infinite possibilities of the universe.
